title: To designate a mountain and icefield in the State of Alaska as the "Mount Stevens" and "Ted Stevens Icefield", respectively.
content: Mount Stevens and Ted Stevens Icefield Designation Act - Directs the United States Board on Geographic Names to designate: (1) a specified unnamed peak in the Alaska Range near Denali Park in Alaska as Mount Stevens. And (2) a specified icefield in the northern Chugach Forest in Alaska as the Ted Stevens Icefield.
